data.meta_description:
5,374 likes, 293 comments - lainaminute on June 22, 2023: "Lynwood California is a relatively small city of only 70,000 people but it has produced HIGHLY IMPACTFUL people from all walks of life. In fact, it should be called L.A.’s Land of Legends. With another edition of the @lataco Neighborhood Project, Let’s get into it! 

Thank you to @mylynwoodca for letting me tell your story through @venuswilliams @lorettasanchez @pattyrodriguez @kevincostnermodernwest @shanemosley @lesdogggg @alfredyankovic @nba_lashes
